        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Pediatric Device Development Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises requirements for the Food and Drug Administration regarding (1) the annual report on the pediatric use of medical devices, and (2) application procedures for pediatric medical devices.</p> <p>The bill also extends the authorizations for (1)the humanitarian device exemption, and (2)demonstration grants for improving pediatric device availability.</p>]]></text>
